            <div class="category-card">
                <h3>AI Integration & Consulting</h3>
                <p>
                    Strategic consulting and AI integration services to help businesses adopt data-driven decision-making.
                </p>
                <ul class="subcategory-list">
                    <li><strong>AI Strategy Development:</strong> Identify opportunities for AI adoption.</li>
                    <li><strong>Custom AI Models:</strong> Develop and train models tailored to your business goals.</li>
                    <li><strong>Integration Services:</strong> Embed AI capabilities into your existing systems.</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="#" class="learn-more-btn">Explore More</a>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>
